library(edgeR)

library("pheatmap")
library("RColorBrewer")

library("ggplot2")
CountTable <- read.csv("kal2.csv", header=TRUE, row.names=1) 
mobDataGroups <- c("Ctrl", "Ctrl", "Ctrl", "siRNA", "siRNA", "siRNA")
d <- DGEList(counts=CountTable,group=factor(mobDataGroups))
d.full <- d
apply(d$counts, 2, sum)
    LT34     LT35     LT36     LT46     LT47     LT48 
 8783220 11496203 10584753  5926961 11690332 12471583 
keep <- rowSums(cpm(d)>100) >= 2
d <- d[keep,]
dim(d)
[1] 2609    6
d$samples$lib.size <- colSums(d$counts)
d$samples
d <- calcNormFactors(d)
plotMDS(d, method="bcv", col=as.numeric(d$samples$group))

#legend("bottomleft", as.character(unique(d$samples$group)), col=1:3, pch=20)
#vsd1 <- varianceStabilizingTransformation(d, blind=FALSE)
d1 <- estimateCommonDisp(d, verbose=T)
Disp = 0.04183 , BCV = 0.2045 
d1 <- estimateTagwiseDisp(d1)
plotBCV(d1)

et12 <- exactTest(d1, pair=c(2,1)) # compare groups 2 and 3
pval = 0.05
l2fc = 1

e_df<-as.data.frame(`et12`)
e_df$Significant.Gene<-"No"
row_number<-which(e_df$PValue<0.05 & abs(e_df$logFC)>1)
e_df$Significant.Gene[row_number]<-"Yes"

e_df$Differential_Gene<-e_df$Significant.Gene
e_df$Differential_Gene[which(e_df$PValue< 0.05 & e_df$logFC> 1)]<-"Up-Regulated"
e_df$Differential_Gene[which(e_df$PValue< 0.05 & e_df$logFC< -1)]<-"Down-Regulated"

sub_e = subset(e_df, abs(e_df$logFC) > 1 & e_df$PValue < .05)

#topTags(et12, n=10)
write.csv(e_df, "edger2.csv", row.names=TRUE)
write.csv(sub_e, "sub_e.csv", row.names=TRUE)

de1 <- decideTestsDGE(et12, adjust.method="BH", p.value=0.05)
summary(de1)
